<h1 id="pdf-to-other-formats">PDF to Other Formats</h1>
<p>PDFs can be converted to:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Word.</li>
  <li>Powerpoint.</li>
  <li>Excel.</li>
  <li>JPG.</li>
</ul>

<p>The process is largely the same as the above conversions.</p>

<h1 id="other-formats-to-pdf">Other Formats to PDF</h1>
<p>Other file formats, namely Word, Powerpoint, Excel and JPG can be converted to PDF.</p>

<h1 id="additional-features">Additional Features</h1>
<p>You can also do the following:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Add page numbers.</li>
  <li>Add a watermark.</li>
  <li>Rotate PDF pages.</li>
  <li>Convert HTML website pages to PDF.</li>
  <li>Unlock a PDF, provided you have the password.</li>
  <li>Protect a PDF with a password.</li>
  <li>Organise a PDF, by sorting, deleting or adding new pages.</li>
  <li>Convert to PDF/A for long term archiving.</li>
  <li>Repairing a PDF, by attempting to recover corrupt data.</li>
</ul>

<h1 id="cost">Cost</h1>
<p>While the service is free, the number of files that can be edited is limited to 1 per tool. For instance, you can only Split 1 PDF at a time. The Merge PDF tool can take 25 PDFs at once. There are Premium and Premium Pro plans for advanced users.</p>

